Citation.sTitle: Densities and speeds of sound for binary mixtures of (1,3-dioxolane or 1,4-dioxane) with (2-methyl-1-propanol or 2-methyl-2-propanol) at the temperatures 298.15 K and 313.15 K
Citation.sAbstract: This paper reports densities and speeds of sound of the binary mixtures 1,3-dioxolane or 1,4-dioxane with 2-methyl-1-propanol or 2-methyl-2-propanol at the temperatures 298.15 K and 313.15 K. Excess volumes and excess isentropic compressibility coefficients have been calculated from experimental data and fitted by means of a Redlich-Kister type equation. The ERAS model has been used to calculate the excess volumes of the four systems at both temperatures.
